	<section id="homepage_news_list" class="homepage-news-list" aria-label="Newslist"><article id="hp_news_article_1" class="cf" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article"><header class="cf"><h1 class="title" itemprop="name headline" id="hp_news_article_1_title">
		<a href="https://4.files.edl.io/b3a0/04/15/20/220424-4a45b042-b14c-4588-b960-524c65341834.pdf">
								Expanded WiFi Coverage Areas
							</a>
						</h1>
					</header><section class="summary cf" itemprop="description" aria-labelledby="hp_news_article_1_title"><p>
								Areas around the outside of Comfort Middle School, High School, and Central Office now have WiFi access. Access is only for students and employees of Comfort ISD. Please stay in your vehicle and observe social distancing protocols.
							</p>
						</section></article><article id="hp_news_article_2" class="cf" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article"><header class="cf"><h1 class="title" itemprop="name headline" id="hp_news_article_2_title">
